<item>
            <title>[FLINK-35820] Converting Duration to String fails for big values</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-35820</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We support &lt;tt&gt;ConfigOption&lt;/tt&gt; with &lt;tt&gt;Duration&lt;/tt&gt; type. The &lt;tt&gt;Configuration&lt;/tt&gt; class can read/write &lt;tt&gt;Duration&lt;/tt&gt; from/to &lt;tt&gt;String&lt;/tt&gt;. Unfortunately the conversion fails for values that do not fit into &lt;tt&gt;long&lt;/tt&gt; after conversion to nanos.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;E.g.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; ConfigOption&amp;lt;Duration&amp;gt; option = ConfigOptions
                .key(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;duration&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
                .durationType()
                .noDefaultValue();
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;final&lt;/span&gt; Configuration config = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Configuration();
        config.set(option, Duration.ofMillis(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Long&lt;/span&gt;.MAX_VALUE));
        config.toFileWritableMap();
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;fails with &lt;tt&gt;java.lang.ArithmeticException: long overflow&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
